Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.98,sign_24_2_Thirteen,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Nineteen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.98,sign_24_1_The_Third_Plate,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:07.15,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama... I am so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:09.61,Main Dialogue - Screening,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Arato Hisako...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:12.21,Main Dialogue - Screening,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kurokiba Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:13.07,Main Dialogue - Screening,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:18.99,Main Dialogue - Screening,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nakiri Alice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:21.45,Main Dialogue - Screening,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All of the above have been expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:23.16,Main Dialogue - Screening,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As well as Mito Ikumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:24.87,Main Dialogue - Screening,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Isami Aldini,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:28.34,Main Dialogue - Screening,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ibusaki Shun, Aoki Daigo, Sato Shoji,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:30.80,Main Dialogue - Screening,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino Yuki, Sakaki Ryoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:32.26,Main Dialogue - Screening,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,and Marui Zenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:35.72,Main Dialogue - Screening,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They have also all been expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.43,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,How could this be? Everyone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:43.18,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. Do you guys really have \Ntime to worry about the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:44.64,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Rindo-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:50.11,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was up against Aldini \Nand Tadokoro-chan... was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:53.72,Main Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.66,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Nakiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:00.28,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:02.45,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:09.25,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:43.62,sign_6424_110_Food_Wars,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(654,1)}Food Wars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:43.62,sign_1937_22_The_Third_Plate,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(654,1)}The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:43.62,sign_1975_23_Totsuki_Train_Ar,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1150,1)}Totsuki Train Arc
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.60,Main Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,Tadokoro-san! Aldini-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:49.56,Main Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was your result?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.69,sign_4003_28_Declaration_of_W,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(467,1)}Declaration of War
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.69,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.86,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.32,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,and dig in to Aldini's dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.49,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.21,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next. Tadokoro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:06.45,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:11.73,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,This one's great, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.75,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,Good! You both pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.40,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:16.71,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:21.25,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,My third-stage exam was to present \Na dish that could make me say "yum."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.46,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're supposed to go head-to-head \Nwith members of the Elite Ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.47,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,but nobody said it had to be a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.31,Main Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:32.27,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Rindo-senpai's such a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.35,Main Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,But if anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:38.53,Main Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,that means that at least you two survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:40.70,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, just us two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.12,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.28,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:50.44,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,All the other rebels that\N went on the other routes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:53.25,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,have already been expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.21,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Isami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:00.56,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Are we just supposed to \Ntake this lying down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:02.80,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Our friends and my brother \Nhave been taken down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:05.22,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,We're just supposed to sit \Nhere and do nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.97,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.96,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:12.31,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira! How can you be so calm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:17.56,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, they had a legit \Ncooking battle and lost, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:22.78,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that really sucks, but it's not like \Ntheir opponent cheated or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:26.15,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,so what's the point of bad-mouthing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:29.77,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're right, but... even then—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:33.16,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,The members of the Elite Ten can \Ndo anything at the school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:35.83,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.04,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.48,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,We have four here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:44.69,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,And over there... Well, Hayama\N got expelled, so they're down one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:47.30,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I guess Nakiri's actually \Na member of the Elite Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.01,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,So that just means that we \Nhave to take four more seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.82,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Soma-kun, um, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.62,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira, what are you going on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.97,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:58.77,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,If we're able to win those seats,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:02.23,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,we can overturn everything, \Nincluding the expulsions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.03,Main Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.02,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:09.74,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to take the majority \Nof the seats on the Elite Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:12.66,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Us right here. Through Shokugeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:11.79,sign_7468_79_Shoku,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shoku
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.12,sign_7468_79_Shoku,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Geki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:16.06,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Take the Elite Ten's seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:20.09,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,You mean... I have to defeat \Na member of the Elite Ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:23.17,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-No way! I can't do that, Soma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.87,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even imagine that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.67,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NYou'll be fine, Tadokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:28.59,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:33.43,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yukihira. A Shokugeki only \Nhappens if both parties agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:36.55,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Central would gain nothing by accepting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:39.13,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,even if they're confident \Nthat they could beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.11,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,They're actually expecting to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.94,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go get some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.83,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,So, hey. Could you give me \Na seat in the Elite Ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.13,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,You always say the craziest things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.84,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,To think that's what you'd say \Nwhen things are like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.49,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, I'm not going to be able to do that,\Nno matter how much fun it sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.77,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:09.05,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.32,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you could do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.26,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.79,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get to you \Ntoo much, Nakiri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:16.50,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably give up on your buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:20.40,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that Yukihira-kun's \Nproposal is extremely unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:24.87,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,And in that case, I can't worry \Nabout my reputation anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:29.20,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,If I go to my father directly and ask \Nhim to rescind everyone's expulsions...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.62,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here, everyone. I'll go \Nto my father right now—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:35.91,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Director Azami, \Nhe's actually here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.37,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,At this location?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:41.58,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,He's been making rounds to the \Nvarious test sites to check up on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.96,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to talk to him, \Nyou should probably hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:47.86,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,He's about to fly off to \Nthe next testing site.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.49,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.60,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Father! I have a request!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.89,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Erina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.86,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,You're still hanging around \Nthat unsavory crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.94,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop being so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:09.90,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,After a few days, they will also be expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.20,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,That is, if no one else decides \Nto take some liberties
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.49,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,with the rules of the exams again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:19.42,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi, you'll be confined \Nto your room at the next exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:24.08,Main Dialogue - Screening,Rind,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, even if I don't kick \Nthem out, someone else will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:28.71,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Father, um... Regarding the students that \Nfailed the stage-three exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:32.80,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Could I ask that you be a little \Nmore merciful toward them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.04,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:38.35,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Alice... Hisako...\NPlease bring everyone back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.77,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,We're running behind. We should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.31,Main Dialogue - Screening,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Azami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:49.15,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all become second-years!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.29,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, Nakiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.83,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,we're just going to have to \Nsettle things plate to plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.79,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.12,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:04.83,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,You sure like talking as though your \Nideas are the only correct ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.25,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,but the fact that I'm standing here right now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:11.53,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,means you haven't been able to \Nprove that you're correct at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:13.30,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to get rid of us that badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:16.65,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you stop with these rigged tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.89,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,and let's settle things once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.72,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,My crew
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.31,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,against yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.90,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we have an all-out battle \Nfor seats in the Elite Ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.99,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,That's an absolutely ridiculous idea, \Neven for you, Yukihira Soma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:41.79,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some advice. If you want to negotiate,\N you need to have something to wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.62,sign_12525_143_Ruffle,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Ruffle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.80,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on now, Nakamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:51.56,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,No need to talk to my \Nprecious only son that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.47,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:01.31,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Saiba Joichiro?! And Senzaemon-dono, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:05.15,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Soma. I heard you got your \Nrevenge on Shiomi's apprentice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:07.40,sign_12979_148_Ruffle_,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(354,1)}Ruffle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.38,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.97,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messin' with my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.94,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always randomly \Npop up from nowhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.51,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Saiba-sama... Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:13.57,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eria,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.28,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Erina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:17.24,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown up so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.38,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to butt in like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:23.57,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,but we need to talk to your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:29.35,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura, I'd say Soma's idea isn't half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:31.55,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we have one of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:32.75,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.46,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,A team battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:41.03,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,A rare but traditional twist on the \NShokugeki where groups of chefs clash...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.89,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,A Régiment de Cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.68,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, a Team Shokugeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:45.68,sign_14002_166_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(343,1)}Team
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.68,sign_14017_167_Shokugeki,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(317,1)}Shokugeki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.16,Main Dialogue - Screening,eri,0000,0000,0000,,Te...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.48,sign_14043_168_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Team
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:46.48,Main Dialogue - Screening,tak,0000,0000,0000,,...am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.00,Main Dialogue - Screening,soma,0000,0000,0000,,Shoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.27,sign_14062_169_Shokugeki,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shokugeki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:47.77,Main Dialogue - Screening,tad,0000,0000,0000,,...geki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:54.44,Main Dialogue - Screening,aza,0000,0000,0000,,Saiba-senpai, you clearly \Ndon't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:59.37,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I took the director's\N seat from Senzaemon-dono,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:10:04.45,sign_14289_175_Totsuki,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.74,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,my plan was 90 percent complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.79,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm currently doing is \Nnothing more than some cleanup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:10.75,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing you could offer would make \Nit worth accepting your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.46,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.98,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Even if...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:18.88,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,I offered to become one of your \Nlittle soldiers if we lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.34,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:23.23,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll abandon all my ideas and beliefs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:27.31,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,and become your servant to help you \Nwith your salvation or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.94,sign_15041_186_Yukihira_Diner,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira\NDiner
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.94,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that also means I'll \Nclose down Yukihira for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.50,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.36,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.23,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:39.82,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,Saiba-senpai, this makes me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.79,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,Today is a wonderful day, a very good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:45.70,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not talk as though \Nyou've already won?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:48.16,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to win, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:52.50,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get our friends back, and we won't \Nlet you to close down Yukihira Diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.71,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:56.55,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to save everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:59.97,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to our day of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.18,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.64,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,We can hash out the details another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:11.85,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:15.37,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get started on \Nyour special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.19,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Training?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:20.60,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,If we take on the Elite Ten right now, \Nthere's no way we're going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.21,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.74,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're going to conserve \Nour strength and prepare for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.99,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Let the training begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:33.48,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,What? A Team Shokugeki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:36.42,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It will be held on Rebun Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:39.33,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world did any of this come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.13,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,A lot has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:46.64,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,Inform the rest of the Elite Ten \Nto continue their journey north.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:50.89,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,We will wipe out the resistance once \Nand for all at the final exam venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:59.57,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,A just world where no chef will \Never have to wander again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:03.48,Main Dialogue - Screening,Aza,0000,0000,0000,,I will save the culinary world and Totsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:09.54,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad, are you seriously going \Nto put Yukihira on the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:09.95,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:14.20,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? First, you shut the place down, \Nand now you're wagering it on a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:16.29,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Could you have some respect for the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.25,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,What? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.99,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,You actually don't think \Nwe're going to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:23.97,sign_17701_221_Ruffle,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,478)}Ruffle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:23.44,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, talk about pathetic! \NYou sure you're my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:24.47,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing up my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.73,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! We're gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.18,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we're gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:31.64,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, this was the only leverage we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:36.06,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I should also probably apologize \Nfor all of this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:37.70,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Dojima-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:42.03,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually the one who arranged for\NJoichiro and Senzaemon-dono to be there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.53,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We've been working in secret for some \Ntime now to come up with a strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:50.49,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Because we knew that if Joichiro was involved,\N Azami would accept the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:54.33,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't blame you if you \Nthink we've been using you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:56.67,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I sincerely apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.92,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:03.78,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, if you or \NSaiba-san hadn't intervened,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:07.01,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't have been able to \Nget this Shokugeki at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:08.89,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,We should actually be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:12.02,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch. This will be our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.23,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let the Azami \NAdministration have their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.23,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:23.82,sign_19110_242_Man,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(214,1)}Man
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:21.35,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,I need to start doing this now, or I \Nwon't be able to deal with the pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:23.82,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,I think it might be a little \Nearly to start doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:28.11,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,Man... Man... Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.87,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I guess you can \Nhave your Mezzaluna back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.11,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a sec, Yukihira!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:30.15,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get that back by beating you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:31.72,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Senzaemon-dono, they are indeed reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:31.72,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,But it's sort of in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:32.68,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,Soma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.37,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The Generation of Prodigies...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.73,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,You better be taking proper care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:37.21,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They are worthy enough to \Nentrust with Totsuki's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:36.17,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,But, no, really, it's in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.21,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:42.37,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do you all know \Nabout Team Shokugekis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:46.34,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,What about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.30,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I can't say I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.35,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard the general rules before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:55.97,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,As Joichiro-san mentioned earlier,\N it's a Shokugeki that's team versus team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:59.89,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Members from each team randomly \Nface off against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:04.10,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Then the victors from each team will \Ncontinue facing off with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:07.95,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,They'll repeat that until one team still \Nhas victors and they win the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.94,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Correct, Chef Dojima?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:13.21,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely. But Team Shokugeki battles
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:16.03,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,have elements that are clearly \Ndifferent from standard Shokugeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:20.46,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the fact that teamwork \Nwill make or break this competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.96,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,Teamwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:25.17,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,But when they face off, \Nit's one-on-one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:30.08,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,In Team Shokugeki, you can help \Nyour teammates with their dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:34.23,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. While you're facing \Noff with your opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.98,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,you can help your teammates \Nif they need assistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.48,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,which results in creating a better team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:42.04,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Which basically means that you're all chefs,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:44.98,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,but also your teammates' support staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:50.64,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So even if you don't stand a chance alone, \Nif you and your team work well together,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:54.08,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,your chances of beating\N the Elite Ten are not zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.54,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But for that to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:15:00.00,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,you need to strengthen your teamwork \Nso it surpasses your opponents'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:04.15,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that tomorrow, you'll be\N having a two-on-two mock battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.05,Main Dialogue - Screening,All,0000,0000,0000,,Mock battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:08.08,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's evaluate all of your \Nindividual strengths, and then—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:10.12,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're gonna draw straws.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:10.76,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.28,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's too random!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.51,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:16.90,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,So, what should the punishment \Nbe for the losing team?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:20.10,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No. This isn't about winning or losing.\N It's just a simulation—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:24.19,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Why don't we have the loser eat \Nthis gross new dish I just came up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:24.92,Main Dialogue - Screening,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:25.93,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Gross dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:27.56,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, a new one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:28.94,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to remember things...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:28.94,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,This one's extra cringe worthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:32.57,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me! After all that time you \Nwere missing, you finally called me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:35.90,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but just said whatever you wanted \Nto say and then hung up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.33,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.13,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself an adult?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.05,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,The adults are fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.71,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Proper adults would...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.71,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,But Chef Dojima is always so calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:45.88,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up, Gin. If you have something \Nto say, say it with your dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:49.34,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on! I'll set you straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.51,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Erina...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:59.72,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried, since you immediately \Nwent back to your cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.24,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:03.94,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't know how to react.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:08.15,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,I want to save everyone. I truly believe \Nthat from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:11.70,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,But in order for that to happen, \Nwe need to defeat the Elite Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.74,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,and my father directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:17.49,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Defy my father? Challenge my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.77,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:22.08,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Just the thought sends shivers\N of dread down my spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:26.13,sign_23585_315_Roughly_Six_Mont,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(479,1)}Roughly Six Months Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.26,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Old,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come, Joichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:30.05,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. How're you doing, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:32.44,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you stopped by \Nthe Polar Star Dormitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:34.68,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to talk with your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:35.93,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.75,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira Soma, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:40.68,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to what \Nhe might do in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:46.07,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice. I had no intention of having \NSoma enroll in Totsuki to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.48,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,I only did because you were so pushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.07,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Old,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.03,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Old,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you back to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.24,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Azami's been making some ominous movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:56.32,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:59.07,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,It's trustworthy information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:03.91,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,In these past few years, he's suddenly \Nbeen developing some connections in Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:07.65,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to speculate that he'll \Nprobably try to contact Totsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.75,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,in some way fairly soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:14.47,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Erina still has fear of that \Nman deep within her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:18.80,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Old,0000,0000,0000,,He'll probably try to take advantage \Nof that and seize control of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.92,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to come up with some kind of plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:25.52,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what we do, it won't \Nbe a fundamental solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:29.77,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who can truly \Nsave your granddaughter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:33.28,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,will probably be classmates whom \Nshe can fight alongside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.11,Flashback Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Soma's generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.66,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Erina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.74,Main Dialogue - Screening,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiba-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:42.83,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,There's a few minor details \Nwe need to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.44,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nakiri-kun! We will commence\N training tonight! Actually, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.37,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,What? Now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:49.63,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We will conduct a \Nthree-on-three mock battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.28,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we don't need to be so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:53.55,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just take this lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.47,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Joichiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:55.76,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:59.84,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how many times that\Nflippant attitude of yours caused me grief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:03.60,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and that's why I said I'll take you \Nup on a challenge as part of the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.64,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this, Nakiri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.15,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,But let's do our best together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:09.48,Main Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,We want to save Arato-san \Nand the others, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.94,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:13.73,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We must save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:18.70,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,And to think I haven't even strengthened \Nmy resolve to face my father yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.12,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:25.45,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,I shall mediate this competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.29,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,The teams will be split as follows:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:32.41,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Tadokoro Megumi, Takumi Aldini,\N and Dojima Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:34.63,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,They will be Team Dojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:34.63,sign_26699_363_Dojima,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Dojima
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:39.00,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira Soma, Nakiri Erina, \Nand Saiba Joichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.97,Main Dialogue Top - Screening,gramp,0000,0000,0000,,They will be Team Saiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.97,sign_26699_363_Dojima,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Saiba
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:45.27,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,The team leaders will be Gin and Joichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:48.06,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,The other two on each team will \Nsupport the preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:51.45,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You better not think of me as \Na student still, Joichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:53.44,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:56.76,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,Nakiri-san and Soma-kun \Nare on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:59.78,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tado,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make sure I don't hold \NChef Dojima and Takumi-kun back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:03.06,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the same team as Saiba-sama, \Nwhom I've admired for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:05.49,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do everything I can to assist him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:08.58,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting us use \Nyour kitchen, Conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:13.72,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,The dish both of your teams will \Nbe making is hachis Parmentier,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:16.86,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,a national dish from France.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:19.26,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,You will have fifty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:23.53,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Hachis Parmentier? I heard of \Nthat back at Master Shinomiya's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:29.08,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dish made with meat sauce, cheese, \Nand pomme purée—basically mashed potatoes—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:30.85,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,baked in an oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.69,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,A dish where various steps of the \Npreparation are very time consuming...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:36.32,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,Even with three of us, we can \Nbarely make it in fifty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.32,sign_28158_384_50_Minutes,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(482,1)}50 Minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:40.53,Main Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,If the chef doesn't split up the\Nduties efficiently, we won't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:44.99,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,As for the rules, you may not say a single \Nword to each other while cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.87,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,And begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:59.09,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?! This is the \Nsame as being blindfolded!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:07.64,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi-kun, how did you know what \NChef Dojima was thinking just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:11.62,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,I see. There's actually nothing different
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.53,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,in this mock battle from any \Nother time we've cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:18.24,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,Think of all of the techniques \Nin my head and invert them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.94,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what the chef is doing carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.20,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,Just like all the times \NI've supported Soma-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.53,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,think about what's going to happen next...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.16,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,and move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:39.00,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they've cleared the first hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:48.18,sign_17701_221_Ruffle,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Ruffle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.45,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold back anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:44.41,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Soma! You need to match your \Nmovements more with mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:48.18,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line! Quit doing steps completely \Nout of order from the basic recipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:50.33,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You're supposed to be my support!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.66,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.27,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!\N And stop messing up my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.73,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,They're talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.44,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hesitate to disqualify you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.15,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:00.11,Main Dialogue - Screening,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.95,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, we had our utensils \Ndown and we weren't cooking,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.20,Main Dialogue - Screening,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,so we should be safe, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.70,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept excuses like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.57,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully. You won't\N get another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:11.41,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, this wouldn't count as training.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.62,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yukihira-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:16.46,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to \Nargue with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:21.25,Main Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Saiba-sama is the leader, so we should \Nbe doing everything we can to support—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:24.68,Main Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, now Nakiri's talking. I'm gonna tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:26.52,Main Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,As if this didn't concern you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.10,Main Dialogue - Screening,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:35.38,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,"But seriously, why is my dad making \Nwhatever he wants to right now?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:39.36,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Soma,0000,0000,0000,,"That's been concerning me, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:44.71,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,The star of hachis Parmentier\N is the meat sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:47.86,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,After frying the meat and herbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:50.96,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,you add in red wine and bullion \Nfor vivid richness and flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:53.56,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,It's the step that takes the longest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:57.96,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,And yet Saiba-sama had started \Nwith the other steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:22:02.42,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Erina,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he following the\N basic steps like Chef Dojima?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:04.48,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Tad,0000,0000,0000,,Anchovies?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:09.05,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,And basil? Those aren't \Ningredients used in this dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.82,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,And that plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:15.93,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,In France, hachis Parmentier is \Nusually served in a gratin dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:18.39,Italics Dialogue - Screening,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,But since he's going to be \Nserving it on a normal plate...
